rows.label: bf05350100_0020
rows.name:
It appears Senator Roderich paid a visit
to the Holy See last night, off the record.

rows.label: bf05350100_0040
rows.name: No. I haven't heard anything from His Majesty.

rows.label: bf05350100_0050
rows.name:
Why now, I wonder? I can't imagine
he was just paying his respects.

rows.label: bf05350100_0060
rows.name:
Do you think it's something to do with
the excavation? Temperantia?

rows.label: bf05350100_0070
rows.name: Hmm. The issue His Majesty mentioned?

rows.label: bf05350100_0080
rows.name:
If that is the case, he must be making covert
deals with the Holy See...
